      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/1/153/2",
      "text": [
        " مُهْلَة مِنَ اللهِ يَهْوِي مَعَ الْغَافِلِينَ، وَيَغْدُومَعَ الْمُذْنِبِينَ، بلاَ سَبِيل قَاصِد، وَلاَ إِمَام قَائِد."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "He has been allowed time by Allāh. He is falling into error along with negligent persons and goes early in the morning with sinners, without any road to lead or any Imām to guide."
        ]
      }
    },
